de.a46.memory.gui
Interface MPanelListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
ButtonbarPanel, MainPanel
public interface MPanelListener

This interface defines three methods, that will be called when events occure on a MPanel. This interface is similar to interface MouseListener.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Till Zoppke
